---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | doticrosst" noindex={true}>
  <section class="bg-charcoal py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Privacy Policy" }]} />
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Who we are</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            doticrosst is a digital agency operated from the United Kingdom. Our website address is https://doticrosst.com.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">What data we collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            When you use our contact form or scoping form, we collect your name, email address,
            phone number (if provided), business name, and the contents of your message. This
            data is processed by Netlify Forms and stored securely on their infrastructure.
            We do not collect any data beyond what you voluntarily submit through these forms.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes. The only cookies that
            may be set are those required for basic website functionality and analytics, as
            described in the Analytics section below.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">How we use your data</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We use the information you provide solely to respond to your enquiry and to discuss
            potential services. Your data helps us understand your project requirements so we
            can provide an accurate quote and scope of work. We do not sell, rent, or share
            your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            If you become a client, we may retain your contact information for the duration of
            our working relationship and for a reasonable period afterwards for record-keeping
            purposes. You can request deletion of your data at any time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Data storage and security</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Form submissions are stored securely by Netlify in their data centres. We access
            this data through Netlify's secure dashboard. We do not store your personal
            information in any additional databases or systems beyond what is necessary
            to deliver our services.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Analytics</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our website. This service
            collects anonymised data such as pages viewed, time spent on the site, referring
            source, and general geographic location. This data is used only to improve the
            content and performance of our website. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect
            this information. You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking by installing the
            Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Third-party services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Our website is hosted on Netlify. Form submissions are processed by Netlify Forms.
            Analytics are provided by Google Analytics. We use Google Fonts for typography,
            which may result in your browser making requests to Google's servers. Each of these
            services has its own privacy policy that governs how they handle data.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            Under GDPR and UK data protection law, you have the right to access, correct,
            or delete your personal data. You also have the right to restrict processing,
            object to processing, and data portability. To exercise any of these rights,
            contact us at craig@doticrosst.com. We will respond to your request within
            30 days.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Data retention</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            We retain form submission data for as long as it is needed to respond to your
            enquiry and for a reasonable period afterwards. If you become a client, we retain
            project-related information for the duration of our relationship and for up to
            six years afterwards for accounting and legal purposes. Analytics data is retained
            according to Google Analytics' default retention settings.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
            For any privacy-related questions, email us at
            <a href="mailto:craig@doticrosst.com" class="font-medium text-accent hover:text-accent-light">craig@doticrosst.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
